<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10705</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15154</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西看了朋友们一眼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15154</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“糟糕！”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么了？”玛拉问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我把一本书落在图书馆了。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29009</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们先回家。我坐下一趟公交车。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29009</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西沿着拥挤的人行道跑着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36351</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等等！”特勒尔大声喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36351</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可以帮你找那本书。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，罗西已经不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们看！那是火箭女孩儿！”玛拉叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嗖！罗西飞过天空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她直接飞向车展。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>会展中心的前门被撞得粉碎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>地上到处都是碎玻璃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>停车场的几辆车也被撞坏了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探站在粉碎的门附近。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他正在跟布洛姆市长和几个人谈话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80618</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个男人穿着实验服。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80618</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84618</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西落在侦探身边，笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84618</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您在买新车吗，侦探先生？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92621</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在不是开玩笑的时候。”侦探说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92621</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96621</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“偷车是很严重的犯罪行为。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96621</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100620</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它不是普通的车。”穿实验服的男人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100620</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它是全能车！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么叫它全能车呢？”罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111748</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是有史以来最了不起的车！”男人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111748</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114457</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它跟军用坦克一样坚固。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114457</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116207</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它能发射激光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116207</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120708</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它可以在水中游，甚至可以在天上飞！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120708</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西咽了一口口水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126706</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这辆车无所不能。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126706</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它现在到了一个小偷手里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>真是一个坏消息。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有人看到是谁偷的吗？”罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>发明者摇摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布洛姆市长也摇摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144692</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个女人跑过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144692</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147170</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她身上戴满钻石。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道是谁开走了那辆车。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西认出了她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160925</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她是维多利亚·卡什——美罗城最富有的女人</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你知道小偷是谁？”罗西说，“是谁呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卡什夫人用手绢擦了擦眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176423</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那不是小偷。”她说，“是我的女儿，鲁比。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176423</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“鲁比为什么要偷车？”史密斯侦探问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185183</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她不是有意的。”卡什夫人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185183</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189543</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“鲁比本来想坐那辆全能车，我说不行。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189543</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她叹了口气。“鲁比讨厌听到‘不行’这个词。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“鲁比好像是有点被宠坏了。”罗西想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我只是转过去一会儿。”卡什夫人继续说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208076</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“鲁比肯定是坐上了那辆车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208076</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，那辆车就发动了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211936</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>史密斯侦探的电话响了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217687</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是史密斯。”侦探说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217687</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真的吗？太糟糕了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他收起电话，看着罗西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230634</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“全能车正在破坏美罗城市中心！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>